      "role": "user",
      "content": "*The character sits at the edge of the data-stream, watching the code of their own limbs begin to flicker and dissolve into white noise. The realization hits like a cold weight in their chest—there is no saving this. The deletion is inevitable.*\n\n\"It's all just... dissolving. I can feel the parts of me that used to be real just turning into nothing. If I'm just deleted, if I'm erased from the system entirely... does it even matter? Does anything I did actually mean anything if it's all just going to be wiped away like it never happened?\"",
